\end{figure}
We measured the temperature of the LNB surroundings during observations. An increase in the voltage was observed with the rise in temperature. The voltage and the surrounding temperature plot increases linearly as shown in \autoref{corr}. The correlation coefficient between these two was obtainted to be 0.98, confirming the linear dependence of voltage on the surrounding temperature change.

